{"tid":651249,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"金管局：美正處加息周期 港息會隨美息逐步上升","createTime":"2018-05-03T03:18:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T04:01:05.000Z","uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9174c51296a731918a913a68f2720a81739766b7","tid":651249,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T03:18:58.000Z","msg":"美聯儲昨日如市場預期維持其貨幣政策不變，市場普遍預期6月會再加息。金管局總裁陳德霖表示，港美息差吸引套息交易，港元轉弱並觸發金管局的弱方兌換保證，資金開始流出港元。隨著資金流出、銀行總結餘減少，港元流動性會逐漸收緊，為港元利息正常化提供更多條件。美國正處於加息周期，在聯繫匯率制度下，港息亦會隨美息逐步上升。<br />\n<br />\n陳德霖提醒，市民必須審慎管理好風險，以應對本地利率及資產市場可能出現波動的情況。"},{"pid":"7d3139032054cceba418784bbe14d1ce0e6ad100","tid":651249,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T03:20:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1525315072419&amp;issue=20180503\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1525315072419%26issue%3D20180503&d=aAR8aiKAwRVGqn2TrRjSN9Wu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=103f4d1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1525315072419&amp;issue=20180503</a>"},{"pid":"667d0517d4d009e26cef78d82fb60f90d0519d2c","tid":651249,"uid":42921,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T03:22:22.000Z","msg":"加得少少就唔好成日講啦，都唔知咩居心，香港人大把錢，無懼加息"},{"pid":"b3a1521d83259a3ae18ce3c1a9d73d31cc5e46c9","tid":651249,"uid":22832,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T03:28:16.000Z","msg":"快d加啦仲講咁多"},{"pid":"088c7d66f065a377844d7b49bc4b4c96be1d51a0","tid":651249,"uid":44171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T03:29:49.000Z","msg":"銀行肯郁先算啦"},{"pid":"11ac0661d7ba4492a1cf5b65a0859ccaa2980589","tid":651249,"uid":10757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T03:31:34.000Z","msg":"你講有春用咩 講得掂班banker?"},{"pid":"e9bcdfafeae3bb125494b3dcd3431e0f381cf240","tid":651249,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s